\begin_inset Formula $w$
\end_inset

 maximizing 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{p}(\cd;w)$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Equivalently, maximize the data log-likelihood:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\minimizer w=\argmax_{w\in\reals^{d}}\sum_{i=1}^{n}\log p(y_{i}\mid x_{i};w)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

